[SHORT DESC]
Hits 2-5 times in one turn.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Hits 2-5 times in one turn. There is a 37.5% chance to hit either 2 or 3 times, and a 12.5% chance to hit either 4 or 5 times. If one hit faints a Substitute, the move will be halted.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>None. This move is awful and its distribution is lackluster.<p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rb/moves/body_slam">Body Slam</a> is a more powerful alternative which boasts a 30% paralyze chance.</p>
<p><a href="/rb/moves/double-edge">Double-Edge</a> is a much stronger option with recoil.</p>